---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Vipul Zope">
  <article class="max-w-[650px] mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">About</h1>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-[var(--color-text)] leading-relaxed">

      <p>i don't know really know much yet. all i know is that the more i learn, the more interesting life becomes.</p>

      <p>i've been a conductor of chaos since i was a kid. as a School Band Leader, i played drums and bass for annual parades — learning the high-stakes timing of live performance. i spent my teens as a <strong>Pro-Gamer</strong> learning strategy under pressure. i model my execution style after Rohit Sharma: calm leadership, selfless strategy, and relentless power when it's time to hit.</p>

      <p>i knew since i was 13 that building was going to be the first chapter of my life. since then, i've dropshipped, ran minecraft servers, played at competitive levels of online gaming, built communities from scratch, managed large-scale recruitment operations, navigated regulatory crises, and scaled teams. i also have a list of dozens of failed ventures that could fill up a whole page.</p>

      <p>after finishing my <strong>Computer Engineering degree (Honours in Data Science)</strong>, i took time off to handle a critical family medical emergency. that chapter is closed, and i'm back in the arena with full force.</p>

    </div>

    <hr class="my-8 border-[var(--color-border)]" />

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-4">Experiences</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium">COO @ Stealth AI Company</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] shrink-0">Present</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">after selling SwipeLabs to an AI company, now operating as COO.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium">Founder @ SwipeLabs.io</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] shrink-0">Past</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">grew to millions in revenue & 25 FT employees before exiting in 2025. served 100+ of the fastest-growing tech companies.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium">Lead @ Placecom</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] shrink-0">Past</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">managed hiring pipelines for IBM, HP, Bentley, Mercedes-Benz, Bosch, TCS and 30+ global giants.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium">Founding Ops @ OP OFFICIALS</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] shrink-0">Past</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">scaled a community to 110k subscribers and 74k discord members.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium">Lead @ StreamEase</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] shrink-0">Past</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">built a network of 78+ creators for Loco, Rooter, JioGames, Chingari and Rumble.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-8 border-[var(--color-border)]" />

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]">
        if you are building something massive in Physical AI, Robotics, or Data Infrastructure — <a href="https://cal.com/vipulzope">let's talk</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm">
        <a href="mailto:contactzope@gmail.com">contactzope@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>

  </article>
</Layout>
